{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_52_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 3話 鼻に蟹がぶら下がってます！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いてっ！　いてててててっ！　蟹が暴れるから\n思わず手を離してしまったが、何が起こってるんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ow! Owwww! The crab’s squirming—\nI let go without thinking—what’s happening!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.91886638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　鼻！\n鼻に蟹がぶら下がってます！　大丈夫ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Your nose!\nThere’s a crab hanging from your nose! Are you okay!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8855330467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.7324487049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "めちゃくちゃ痛いぞ！？　は、鼻がもげるっ！\nひ～助けてくれ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It hurts like crazy!? M-my nose is going to rip off!\nH-Help meee!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "待ってて下さい、今、蟹を引っ張りますから……！\n離しなさい、この～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold still‚ I’ll pull the crab off…!\nLet go‚ you~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9189121245,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4153.084151000002,
          "startTime": 26.9189121245
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6667.5053597999995,
          "startTime": 29.4333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7900.838693200001,
          "startTime": 30.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.9189121245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いててててて！　怜、ストップ、ストップ！\n鼻が本当にもげるぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Owwww! Rei‚ stop‚ stop!\nMy nose is seriously going to rip off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5135615346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.123176193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ぷっ……あはははは！　鼻に蟹がぶら下がるって……\n聞いたことないですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pfft… ahahaha! A crab hanging from someone’s nose…\nI’ve never heard of that before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9144236563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "怜……さっきからずっと笑ってるな\n俺はまだ鼻の感覚がないんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei… you’ve been laughing this whole time.\nI still can’t feel my nose…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.600001335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3167357759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ、蟹がぶら下がってくれたおかげで\n一番大きい蟹をゲット出来たんですから、お手柄ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ thanks to that crab hanging on‚\nwe managed to get the biggest one—so good job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5213169732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.0667355852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、掴み取りでこんな取り方をしたのは\n初めてだってお店の人も言ってましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ the staff said\nthey’ve never seen anyone catch one like that before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3546503065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "それにあんなに大きくて美味しい蟹は初めて食べました\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’ve never eaten such a big and delicious crab before.\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0546503065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.1083053585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、蟹を二人占めしたってバレたら\nみんなに怒られそうだから内緒にして下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ if anyone finds out we kept that crab to ourselves‚\nthey’ll probably scold us—so let’s keep it a secret‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4879836398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、鼻に蟹がぶら下がったなんて知られたら\n一生いじられ続けるからな……怜も内緒で頼むよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ if people find out a crab hung from my nose‚\nI’ll never hear the end of it… You keep it secret too‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5333367029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 98.6826981541
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 98.6826981541
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 99.2367329596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ここがお土産コーナーか……\n怜、自分へのお土産も買っていいからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is the souvenir section…\nRei‚ you can get something for yourself too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6333367029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "はい。……結構変わったお土産があるんですね\nメロン味とかキャビア味のキャラメル……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. …There are some pretty unusual souvenirs here.\nMelon-flavored and even caviar-flavored caramels…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1329915363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 118.0103880879
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "み、味噌ラーメン味……！？\nこれは愛が喜びそうだけど、美味しいのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-miso ramen flavor…!?\nAi might like this‚ but I wonder if it actually tastes good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5663248697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなへのお土産を買おうと\n思ったけど、こんなに沢山あったら迷ってしまうわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking of buying souvenirs for everyone at Hoshimi Pro‚\nbut with this many choices‚ it’s hard to decide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4329915363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 134.8262611385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、この生チョコ……って\n凄い荷物ですね！？　そんなに買うんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san‚ this fresh chocolate—wait‚\nthat’s a lot of bags! You bought that much!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5329915363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ……星見プロのみんなとお世話になった\n人達へのお土産を買っていたらこんなことに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah… once I started buying for everyone at Hoshimi Pro\nand the people who’ve helped us‚ it kind of turned into this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3333367029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 151.3000480013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですね。それにしても……なんですか\nこの謎の干物は？　なんの魚なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. But still… what is this\nmysterious dried fish? What kind is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6714497248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 163.2000477152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "これは沙季へのお土産だ。沙季はくさやが好きだから\n喜んでくれると思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s for Saki. She likes kusaya‚\nso I figured she’d be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.0566075776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、このまりも飼育セットなんていいと思わないか？\nすずがペットをほしがってたからな。喜ぶぞこれは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And look—doesn’t this marimo growing kit seem nice?\nSuzu wanted a pet‚ so she’ll love this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.3000033695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 178.0215896286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "それ……多分すずが求めてるペットとは違う\n気がしますけど……はぁ。仕方ないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… think that’s probably not the kind of pet\nSuzu meant… sigh. It can’t be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.6263249714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にお土産を選びましょう\n{user}さんには任せられません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s choose the souvenirs together.\nI can’t leave this to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.8929967243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 194.5113225298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
